creator: Livelaboratorio Oy
descriptionHtml:
G Livelab Helsinki
Yrjönkatu 3, Helsinki Finland

G Livelab Tampere
Puutarhakatu 1, Tampere Finland

Take your live music experience to the next level:
- explore upcoming events
- buy tickets and share them inside the App
- experience quality live music across all genres: pop, rock, jazz, folk & classical
- enjoy unmatched hi-fi live sound and visuals

Buy drinks & food on the App during the event:
- pick your choice of alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages
- select food from menus of nearby restaurants
- easy and secure one-click order and payment, never leaving the application - or your table
- fast delivery to your table or seat

More cool benefits:
- special deals & discounts for the App users
- give tickets as gifts
- store your tickets & all the receipts in the application
descriptionShort: G Livelab The future of live music. Tickets, food and drinks on your mobile.
